(47, 1, '2019-12-08 10:13:58', '2019-12-08 10:13:58', '<h2>Product information</h2>\r\n<div class="columns accordion-section brd-gray" data-automation-id="accordion-section-Overview">\r\n<div class="column is-4">\r\n<div class="title">Overview</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="column is-8 accordion-with-bot-border brd-gray" data-automation-id="accordion-section-details-Overview">\r\n<ul data-automation-id="bullets">\r\n 	<li class="note">Dimensions: 85L x 33W x 34H in.; Seat height: 21 in.</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">Free fabric swatches available! Call 888.880.4884</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">Kiln-dried solid wood legs in maple finish</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">Plywood and solid wood frame</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">Lightly textured, 100% polyester fabric upholstery in your choice of color</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">Foam-encased pocketed seat coils</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">Sinuous no-sag springs</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">Hand-tufted details and attached back cushions</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">Fixed, tight back and seat cushions (zippers for fluffing fill)</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">Mid-century modern style</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">Part of the Carter Collection</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">Hayneedle exclusive design</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="columns accordion-section brd-gray" data-automation-id="accordion-section-What\'s Included">\r\n<div class="column is-4"></div>\r\n<div class="column is-8 accordion-with-bot-border brd-gray" data-automation-id="accordion-section-details-What\'s Included">\r\n<div></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="columns accordion-section brd-gray" data-automation-id="accordion-section-Description">\r\n<div class="column is-4">\r\n<div class="title">Description</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="column is-8 accordion-with-bot-border brd-gray" data-automation-id="accordion-section-details-Description">\r\n<div class="is-spacious">\r\n\r\nWe\'re as obsessed with mid-century style as they come, and that\'s why we\'re thrilled to introduce you to our <strong>Belham Living Carter Sofa.</strong> With a tight, tufted back sans cushions, a smooth silhouette from the base to the arms and top, and those iconic wood tapered legs, this sofa is today\'s homage to fabulous 50s style.\r\n\r\nThe quality and value of this Hayneedle exclusive begins with kiln-dried solid wood. Kiln-drying is a fast method of drying wood at high heat; this ensures the wood won\'t expand or contract, and it kills any possibility of insects. The Carter\'s solid wood, tapered legs are finished in a versatile maple stain, and they elevate the sofa for that classic mid-mod look.\r\n\r\nWith this kind of on-trend yet lasting style, we went with a lightly textured upholstery that\'s polyester for easy care and incredible durability. Tightly upholstered and hand-tufted, the fabric provides real versatility - a neutral color allows you to add any number of colors and patterns in decorative pillows and throws. With 1.8-pound foam density, the attached seat cushions and tightly upholstered back provide a decidedly firm seat that will hold up year after year. Zippers do allow you to access the cushions for airing and fluffing.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Belham Living Carter Sofa', 'Belham Living Carter Sofa\r\n\r\nThe quality and value of this Hayneedle exclusive begins with kiln-dried solid wood. Kiln-drying is a fast method of drying wood at high heat; this ensures the wood won\'t expand or contract, and it kills any possibility of insects. The Carter\'s solid wood, tapered legs are finished in a versatile maple stain, and they elevate the sofa for that classic mid-mod look.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'belham-living-carter-sofa', '', '', '2019-12-28 08:34:01', '2019-12-28 08:34:01', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=47', 0, 'product', '', 0),
