(49, 1, '2019-12-08 10:22:22', '2019-12-08 10:22:22', '<div class="column is-4">\r\n<h2>Product description</h2>\r\n<div class="title">Overview</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="column is-8 accordion-with-bot-border brd-gray" data-automation-id="accordion-section-details-Overview">\r\n<ul data-automation-id="bullets">\r\n 	<li class="note">Overall dimensions: 95.75W x 40.75D x 36.25H in.</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">Seat dimensions: 85.7W x 26D x 21H in.</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">Frame made from solid birch and engineered wood</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">Light gray upholstery made from 100% wrap-knit polyester</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">Sinuous spring seat topped with pocket coil spring cushions</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">Padded with 1.8-lb. density foam for medium-plush comfort</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">4 matching throw pillows included</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">Removable cushions for easy spot cleaning</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">Rubberwood legs</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">250-lb. weight capacity</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">Part of the Hayden Hill Collection</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="column is-4">\r\n<div class="title">Description</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="column is-8 accordion-with-bot-border brd-gray" data-automation-id="accordion-section-details-Description">\r\n<div class="is-spacious">\r\n\r\nThe <strong>Belham Living Hayden Hill Sofa</strong>\'s inviting cushions, plush pillows, and soothing gray tones beckon you and your family home. Up to three people can fit comfortably on the seats - more if you don\'t mind getting a little snug. This couch is upholstered with 100% wrap-knit polyester over padded foam and fiber batting. Sinuous springs and individual pocket coils support your seat cushions, providing lasting bounce and all-over comfort. For durability, the frame is made from birch wood and engineered plywood.\r\n\r\nFour complementary throw pillows are included. To create a cohesive living room, look to the other furniture in Belham Living\'s Hayden Hill Collection (sold separately).\r\n\r\n<strong>Additional Size Information:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Throw pillow (each): 21L x 21W in.</li>\r\n 	<li>Arms: 8.5W x 25.5H in.</li>\r\n 	<li>Leg height: 2.2 in.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Belham Living Hayden Hill Sofa', '<strong>Belham Living Hayden Hill Sofa</strong>\r\n\r\nThe \'s inviting cushions, plush pillows, and soothing gray tones beckon you and your family home. Up to three people can fit comfortably on the seats - more if you don\'t mind getting a little snug. This couch is upholstered with 100% wrap-knit polyester over padded foam and fiber batting. Sinuous springs and individual pocket coils support your seat cushions, providing lasting bounce and all-over comfort. For durability, the frame is made from birch wood and engineered plywood.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'belham-living-hayden-hill-sofa', '', '', '2019-12-11 05:49:40', '2019-12-11 05:49:40', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=49', 0, 'product', '', 0),
