(51, 1, '2019-12-08 10:25:47', '2019-12-08 10:25:47', '<h2>Product Description</h2>\r\n<div class="column is-4">\r\n<div class="title">Overview</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="column is-8 accordion-with-bot-border brd-gray" data-automation-id="accordion-section-details-Overview">\r\n<ul data-automation-id="bullets">\r\n 	<li class="note">Dimensions: 82.7W x 33.1D x 32.7H in.</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">Seat dimensions: 74.6W x 20.2D in.</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">Constructed with a solid rubberwood frame</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">Easy-care brushed polyester upholstery</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">Supportive webbed suspension</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">Cushions padded with foam and batting</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">Removable cushion covers</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">Weight capacity: 500 lbs.</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">Solid wood legs with protective rubber glides</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">Super simple assembly required: just attach legs</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">Part of the exclusive MoDRN Mid-Century Revival Collection</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class="column is-4">\r\n<div class="title">Description</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="column is-8 accordion-with-bot-border brd-gray" data-automation-id="accordion-section-details-Description">\r\n<div class="is-spacious">\r\n\r\nReinvent your living room with the <strong>MoDRN Mid-Century Pullman Sofa</strong> as its centerpiece. This sofa offers a new take on mid-century style without straying too far from the aesthetic\'s influences. The angled legs, simple shapes, and wood tones you love are very much present, but they\'re reimagined in a refreshing way.\r\n\r\nEvery item in the Mid-Century Revival selection is designed and constructed with care and thoughtfulness. Take the Pullman Sofa\'s frame, which is built from rubberwood - a type of wood we appreciate not just for its beauty and durability, but for its eco-friendly bonafides as well. On top of the frame, easy-care brushed polyester upholstery has the look and feel of tweed, and it comes in your choice of available colors so you can find the best match for your living room. The sofa\'s cushions and cushion covers are removable for even easier care.\r\n\r\nWhether you\'re just dipping your toes into mid-century style or your home looks like it could blend right into a Mad Men episode, MoDRN\'s Mid-Century Revival Collection will offer something to suit your fancy. Pair this couch with the MoDRN Mid-Century Pullman Apartment Sofa and the MoDRN Mid-Century Pullman Bench to pull your living room together.\r\n\r\n<strong>The MoDRN Mid-Century Revival Collection</strong>\r\nThe MoDRN Mid-Century Revival Collection breathes new life into throw-back trends. The clean-lined pieces are inspired by Danish design, which celebrates function ahead of form. Pale wood tones and open, geometric wire frames give your space a style that looks to the future with a nod to the past.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'MoDRN Mid-Century Pullman Sofa', '<strong>MoDRN Mid-Century Pullman Sofa</strong>\r\n\r\nReinvent your living room with the <strong>MoDRN Mid-Century Pullman Sofa</strong> as its centerpiece. This sofa offers a new take on mid-century style without straying too far from the aesthetic\'s influences. The angled legs, simple shapes, and wood tones you love are very much present, but they\'re reimagined in a refreshing way.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'modrn-mid-century-pullman-sofa', '', '', '2019-12-11 07:30:29', '2019-12-11 07:30:29', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=51', 0, 'product', '', 0),
