(55, 1, '2019-12-08 10:34:11', '2019-12-08 10:34:11', '<div class="columns accordion-section brd-gray" data-automation-id="accordion-section-Overview">\r\n<div class="column is-4">\r\n<h2>Product description</h2>\r\n<div class="title">Overview</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="column is-8 accordion-with-bot-border brd-gray" data-automation-id="accordion-section-details-Overview">\r\n<ul data-automation-id="bullets">\r\n 	<li class="note">Dimensions: 92W x 43Wx 39H in.</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">Frame is constructed of birch and plywood</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">100% polyester upholstery in beige</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">Sinuous spring seats with individually wrapped pocket coils</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">1.8-lb. density foam cushions offer medium plush comfort</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">Split-style back cushions</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">Removable cushions with zippered covers</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">Tapered block legs are made of rubberwood</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">Pair with other items from the Millport Collection</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">Designed by Hayneedle</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="columns accordion-section brd-gray" data-automation-id="accordion-section-What\'s Included">\r\n<div class="column is-4"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="columns accordion-section brd-gray" data-automation-id="accordion-section-Description">\r\n<div class="column is-4">\r\n<div class="title">Description</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="column is-8 accordion-with-bot-border brd-gray" data-automation-id="accordion-section-details-Description">\r\n<div class="is-spacious">\r\n\r\nA simple, comfortable design gives the <strong>Belham Living Millport Sofa</strong> a transitional look that will fit in with nearly any living room décor style. This sofa is durably constructed from the ground up. The birch and plywood frame is supported by tapered block legs, which are made of rubberwood. Sinuous spring seats are topped with removable seat and back cushions. At t