(61, 1, '2019-12-08 10:39:23', '2019-12-08 10:39:23', '<h2>Product description</h2>\r\n<div class="columns accordion-section brd-gray" data-automation-id="accordion-section-Overview">\r\n<div class="column is-4">\r\n<div class="title">Overview</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="column is-8 accordion-with-bot-border brd-gray" data-automation-id="accordion-section-details-Overview">\r\n<ul data-automation-id="bullets">\r\n 	<li class="note">Dimensions: 92W x 40D x 34H in.</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">Sofa and 4 toss pillows</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">Kiln-dried hardwood frame</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">Corner-blocked, nailed, and glued frame</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">100% polyester fabric upholstery in ivory</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">8-gauge, narrow-loop sinuous springs</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">6.5 in. thick, 1.8-density foam seating</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">3-in. high-density foam core; 1.5-in. high-resiliency foam top</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">Padded, tufted seat, back, and arms</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">Rolled arms and back, nailhead accenting, wood-trimmed base</li>\r\n 	<li class="note">Clean with water-based shampoo or foam upholstery cleaner</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="columns accordion-section brd-gray" data-automation-id="accordion-section-What\'s Included">\r\n<div class="column is-4"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="columns accordion-section brd-gray" data-automation-id="accordion-section-Description">\r\n<div class="column is-4">\r\n<div class="title">Description</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="column is-8 accordion-with-bot-border brd-gray" data-automation-id="accordion-section-details-Description">\r\n<div class="is-spacious">\r\n\r\nInvite timeless style and elegance into your home by way of the <strong>Belham Living Barron Sofa</strong>. Form and function meet beautifully in the design of this classic sofa: Its kiln-dried hardwood frame is corner-blocked, nailed, and glued to ensure long-lasting support while an impressive combinat