(135, 1, '2019-12-11 07:45:01', '2019-12-11 07:45:01', '<!-- wp:image {"id":75,"sizeSlug":"large"} -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img src="blob:http://localhost/11d674d7-9970-4961-9a62-d88cd9c33c83" alt="" class="wp-image-75"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We are bringing you two new exclusive collections from renowned British furniture brand ercol.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The exclusive collections, Askett and Hughenden, include a range of oak dining tables, dining chairs and sideboards, as well as an elegantly understated living room suite.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Harveys’ Head of Buying, Kellie Oliver, said: “We have identified some key trends for 2020 that the new Ercol range ties perfectly into. Ercol’s quality and craftsmanship has been refined over its 100-year heritage, so it’s a welcome addition to our extensive furniture range at Harveys.”</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>ASKETT</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This oak collection features smooth lines and a beautiful end grain finish achieved with traditional crafting techniques, delivering a classic yet contemporary look. It includes a flip-top and medium extending dining table, perfect for compact homes.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>“The Askett collection is very on trend for 2020, with clean lines and contemporary design set to continue being popular,” said Kellie Oliver, Head of Buying for Harveys.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>HUGHENDEN</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The made-to-order Hughenden collection is perfect for those looking for a touch of understated elegance in their living room. The rich palette of contemporary fabrics complement each other beautifully for a refined finish.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:p